</head><body><header class="site-header"><nav class="nav"><a class="brand" href="index.html"><strong>R.A. Crawford</strong><span>Epic Fantasy Author</span></a><button class="menu-btn">☰</button><div class="links"><a class="" href="index.html">Home</a><a class="active" href="books.html">Books</a><a class="" href="world.html">World</a><a class="" href="about.html">About</a><a class="" href="contact.html">Contact</a></div></nav></header><main><section class="page-hero"><h1>Books</h1></section><section class="section"><div class="grid-2"><div><img class="book-cover" src="assets/cover.jpg" alt="The War of Feather and Shadow book cover"></div><div><p class="kicker">Book One</p><h2>The War of Feather and Shadow</h2><p><strong>Book One of The Raven's Heir Trilogy</strong></p><p>A crown divides. A bloodline rises. A war begins.</p><p>As the old Houses tighten their grip and forgotten powers stir beneath the world, one heir must decide whether destiny is a chain — or a blade.</p><a class="btn primary" href="contact.html">Coming Soon</a></div></div></section></main><footer class="footer">© 2026 R.A. Crawford. All rights reserved.</footer>
<script>
const btn=document.querySelector('.menu-btn');const links=document.querySelector('.links');if(btn&&links){btn.addEventListener('click',()=>links.classList.toggle('open'));}
function makeFeather(){const f=document.createElement('div');f.className='feather';f.style.left=Math.random()*100+'vw';f.style.animationDuration=(8+Math.random()*8)+'s';f.style.opacity=0.35+Math.random()*0.55;f.style.transform=`rotate(${Math.random()*180}deg)`;f.style.width=(10+Math.random()*18)+'px';f.style.height=(32+Math.random()*32)+'px';document.body.appendChild(f);setTimeout(()=>f.remove(),17000)}
setInterval(makeFeather,900);for(let i=0;i<10;i++)setTimeout(makeFeather,i*450);
</script>
